name: 乔·卡明斯

last_movies.title: 安东尼·波登：未知之旅 第三季

introduction: Joe Cummings is an actor, composer, and production consultant known for Sang Krasue 2 (2023), The Cave (2019), The Attic (2017), and Petchakat (2014). After playing in a succession of garage bands in high school and college, he started writing for newspapers and magazines in the San Francisco area. He later moved to Bangkok, where he connected with the local and international film production scene, working as an actor, script editor, location scout, and location manager for such films as The Elephant King (2006) and Croc (2007). More recently Joe began composing music for feature films and TV, including Sniper 3 (2004), Petchakat (2014), Anthony Bourdain: Parts Unknown (2013), The Attic (2017) and The Cave (2019).
